    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon, throw the watery seeds away</p><p>Grate the <strong>deseeded cucumber</strong> and squeeze out any excess water</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
