    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>into slices</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> leaves from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>remaining red wine vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>cucumber & tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
