    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cucumber</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>remaining grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), most of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> (save the rest for garnish!), your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>tzatziki</strong></p>",
